== 余震 ==
首次[[余震|余震]]发生在主震后18分钟，达到6.2级<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2010tfar.php |title=Magnitude 6.2 - OFFSHORE MAULE, CHILE |accessdate=2010-02-28 |archive-date=2010-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100302200319/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2010tfar.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>，第二次余震达到6.0级，发生在主震后38分钟<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2010tfav.php |title=Magnitude 6.0 - OFFSHORE VALPARAISO, CHILE |accessdate=2010-02-28 |archive-date=2010-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100302200324/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2010tfav.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美国地质调查局说，预计会有大量强烈的余震发生。截至27日22时（UTC），已发生59次5级以上余震<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/aftershocks/?code=2010tfan |title=Aftershock Mapping |accessdate=2010-02-28 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305035820/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/aftershocks/?code=2010tfan |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Maps/10/285_-35_eqs.php |title=Earthquake List for 10-degree Map Centered at 35°S, 75°W |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100101120852/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Maps/10/285_-35_eqs.php |archivedate=2010-01-01 |accessdate=2010-02-28 }}</ref>，其中至少6次超過6級<!--阿根廷的不算餘震-->，最強一次達6.9级。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2010tfa7.php |title=Magnitude 6.9 - OFF THE COAST OF BIO-BIO, CHILE |accessdate=2010-02-28 |archive-date=2010-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100302200303/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2010tfa7.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>

28日4时29分（UTC），在[[阿根廷|阿根廷]][[门多萨省|门多萨省]]发生5.0级地震<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2010tgbr.php |title=Magnitude 5.0 - MENDOZA, ARGENTINA |accessdate=2010-02-28 |archive-date=2010-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100303144716/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2010tgbr.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>，暂未确定是否为此次地震的余震。

== 地震前後全球地震情况 ==
地震发生前后1天内在全球多个地震带上均发生了多次5级以上地震，最大达7.0级。
* 地震發生前几个小时（[[UTC|UTC]] 2月26日20时31分），[[日本|日本]][[琉球群岛|琉球群岛]][[冲绳县|冲绳县]]以东海域发生7.0级地震<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2010teb2.php |title=Magnitude 7.0 - RYUKYU ISLANDS, JAPAN |accessdate=2010-02-28 |archive-date=2010-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100228215634/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2010teb2.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後發生最大为5.1級的餘震（UTC 2月27日0時48分）。而[[菲律宾|菲律宾]][[棉兰老岛|棉兰老岛]]（UTC 2月26日8时37分及16时18分）、[[印度尼西亚|印度尼西亚]][[苏拉威西岛|苏拉威西岛]]（UTC 2月26日4时41分）、[[中国|中国]][[西藏|西藏]][[珠穆朗玛峰|珠穆朗玛峰]]北坡（UTC 2月26日4时42分）、[[台灣|台灣]][[花蓮縣|花蓮]]外海（UTC 2月26日1时7分）及[[太平洋|中太平洋]]南部[[布韦岛|布韦岛]]（UTC 2月26日0时11分）均发生了5级以上地震。<!--5级以下地震无需写出，否则太多了！已在讨论页说明。-->
* 地震发生後幾小時，[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]北部[[萨尔塔省|萨尔塔省]]發生的6.3級地震（UTC 2月27日15时45分）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2010tfc3.php |title=Magnitude 6.3 - SALTA, ARGENTINA |accessdate=2010-02-28 |archive-date=2010-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100302200417/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2010tfc3.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[秘魯|秘魯]]南部[[伊卡大区|伊卡大区]]發生的4.2級地震（2月27日UTC 14時33分）均为独立地震，而非本次地震的余震。

